ic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8db0e9d5-4389-47db-bb7d-39c35ccb5340\">통증과 체형을 한번에!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-f1438296-6fb9-45e4-8ad6-58101f9de72e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b829ec75-c2fe-487d-8a85-c3cebf2c9d90\">몸과 마음의 균형!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-8c6c90a1-d735-4d37-8fda-80df68a2bf92\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-aacdf33c-d607-4ce4-a630-33b17d78d3e2\">안녕하세요, 이수한의원입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-a3d9377f-7cfe-4cb3-879d-fe6eb07d3d4c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d7061274-f3ba-4600-ad45-cb3fd22d7b5f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-95efc435-b673-47a8-a2e5-622021e82b11\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2afe978f-815a-4f66-a70d-fc33c0ba25e1\">오늘은 통증해결 한방토크 열여덟 번째 시간,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-37b53726-a35f-43de-8935-ff67693a9f44\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e6d1a4e4-9f34-4e1c-b0b1-ec9412e78f16\"><b>&#x27;MRI부터 찾는 사람들&#x27;</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=